<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ages ago, in May 2022, VMware Inc. <a href=3D"=
https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33194519.283415/aHR0cHM6Ly93d=
3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzExMjQ2MTAvMDAwMTE5MzEyNTIyMTYxMTY4=
L2QzNjIyNTZkZXg5OTEuaHRt/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB811eb754" itemprop=3D"Sto=
ryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; =
text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-c=
olor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> signed=
 a deal</a> to be acquired by Broadcom Inc. The deal was for half cash, hal=
f stock, and=C2=A0VMware shareholders <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomber=
gbusiness.com/click/33194519.283415/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9=
lZGdhci9kYXRhLzExMjQ2MTAvMDAwMTE0MDM2MTIyMDM1ODMzL255MjAwMDU0NTR4MV9kZWZtMT=
RhLmh0bQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBa0d1fe01" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscop=
e=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration:=
 none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; b=
order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> could choose</a> to ta=
ke either $142.50 in cash or 0.2520 shares of Broadcom per VMware share. Th=
e day before the announcement, Broadcom=E2=80=99s stock closed at $531.63, =
making the stock consideration worth about $133.97 and the cash a better de=
al. Last week, Broadcom closed at $838.36, making the stock consideration w=
orth about $211.27 and a=C2=A0<em>much=C2=A0</em>better deal.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But Broadcom only agreed to pay half the consi=
deration in cash: If everyone chooses stock (as you=E2=80=99d expect), then=
 they all get prorated and end up with=C2=A0half cash and half stock. (That=
 is, roughly, $71.25 in cash and $105.63 worth of stock.) Or if almost ever=
yone chooses stock, but some people choose cash, then the cash people get a=
ll cash and the stock people get a little bit more than half stock. And if =
you don=E2=80=99t choose at all, you get whatever nobody else wants (here, =
cash).</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The merger was supposed to close today, but it=
 didn=E2=80=99t. Broadcom and VMware <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/33194519.283415/aHR0cHM6Ly9pci52bXdhcmUuY29tL3dlYnNpdGVz=
L3Ztd2FyZS9FbmdsaXNoLzIxMjAvdXMtcHJlc3MtcmVsZWFzZS5odG1sP2FpcnBvcnROZXdzSUQ=
