 bad accidents=E2=80=9D then nebbishy awkward oversharing charm is going to=
 come across better than slick charm.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Still, I mean. All those glowing reviews are l=
ike =E2=80=9CI thought he was 10,000% guilty, but now I only think he=E2=80=
=99s 99.99% guilty.=E2=80=9D And today he is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.b=
